name: Elevation03
description:
This NFT re-generates itself each time it is sold! A history of all items accumulated are available on this interactive NFT itself. The generated art is deterministic yet unpredictable depending on the buyers.
@greweb is happy to deliver physical plots for anyone who wants the item number you want under the condition you have bought it once. The more the NFT gets bought, the more editions there will be. Feel free to PM me to ask for more information about this.
